author: Kynix @KynixXBT
text: Sold another 40% of my $Bonk at 0.000036, only 30% remaining. I expect it to repeat what it did in November: Some kind of 5 Wave Impulse, leading to a bearish divergence which ends the uptrend. Percentage-wise, this move is getting quite similar with maybe 25% more upside left.
